flowRoot.flowPara: Bubbles appear in the top right corner of the display and disappear automatically.
Badges appear on icons in the dock. They are dismissed by taking action within the app.
Sounds play once when a new notification arrives. Music and other sounds are temporarily turned down.

text.tspan: elementary OS is in Do Not Disturb mode

flowRoot.flowPara: While in Do Not Disturb mode, notifications and alerts will be hidden and notification sounds will be silenced.
System notifications, such as volume and display brightness, will be unaffected.

text.tspan: You have no apps that use notifications

flowRoot.flowPara: Notifications preferences are for configuring which apps make use of notifications, for changing how an app's notifications appear, and for setting when you don't want to be disturbed by notifications.
When apps are installed that have notification options they will automatically appear here.
